high_descs: Turn to your right and go into the kitchen, just past the counter, then turn left and go to the small counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the fork near the edge of the counter, to the left of the stove.
Move over to your right so that you are directly in front of the stove.
Place the fork in the fry pan that is on the front, right burner of the stove.
Pick up the fry pan with the fork inside it.
Turn to your left and go to the counter across from the yellow chairs.
Place the fry pan with the fork inside on the counter top, to the left of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a fry pan containing a fork on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and go forward past the kitchen counter, then turn left to go to the counter adjacent to the stove.
Pick up the fork on the counter adjacent to the stove.
Turn right and go to the stove next to you.
Put the fork on the pan, on the stove.
Pick up the pan from the stove.
Turn left and go forward to the counter.
Put the pan on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a fork in it on the counter.

high_descs: Go to the counter left of the stove
Pick up the fork
Go to the stove
Put the fork in the pan on the right
Pick up the pan
Go to the counter on the left
Put the pan on the countertop
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a fork in it on the countertop
